Rhythmbox MicroBlogger 0.4

	Ali Vakilzade <ali.vakilzade [--at--] gmail [--dot--] com>

DESCRIPTION

  A simple plugin to send current music information to a micro blogging service

INSTALL
  0- If you use ArchLinux install from here and jump to step 2
    http://aur.archlinux.org/packages.php?ID=40403

  1-
    cd ~/.gnome2/rhythmbox/plugins/
    git clone git://github.com/aliva/rhythmbox-microblogger.git

  2- run/restart Rhythmbox active this plugin 'microblogger' and add accounts!

  3- now a button will appear in rhythmbox toolbar. use that for sending notice

  4- for more info check our identica page <http://identi.ca/group/rhythmboxmicroblogger>

LICENSE

  microblogger is distributed under the GPL Version 3.


